<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>mạtstgẖrbsẖ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 (mạtstgẖrbsẖ
 lw ạ̉ḥlạmk fy ạlṣlạẗ .. bʿd zmạn ạtḥqqt
 mạtstgẖrbsẖ
 lw ynạbyʿ sqt ạlạ̉rạḍy .. bʿd mạ ạtsẖqqt
 mạtstgẖrbsẖ)2

[V2]
 lw ạ̹ydyn fy ạldmwʿ .. lmst ktạfk
 sẖjʿt nfsk wqmt .. wʿly htạfk
 lw ẓrwfk hy hy .. lkn ḥznk mạkmlsẖ
 lạ mạtstgẖrbsẖ

[V3]
 (mạtstgẖrbsẖ
 lw fyh nạs kạnt rạfḍẗ ḥbh .. wạlnhạrdh btʿbdh
 mạtstgẖrbsẖ
 lw qsạwẗ ạlqlb dạbt .. lmạ lmsh wjddh
 mạtstgẖrbsẖ)2

[V4]
 lw sjwn ạtftḥt .. wdkẖlhạ nwrh
 bdd ạlạ̉ḥzạn .. bfyḍ ynbwʿ srwrh
 wʿ ạlṣkẖrẗ tẖbt ạlrjl .. ạlly kạnt mạbtqdrsẖ
 mạtstgẖrbsẖ

[V5]
 ʿly ạ̹ymạnk wḥbk llmsyạ
 ḥṭ tẖqtk wạtrmy ʿly̱ ạlḥbyb
 dy mḥbth wqdrth dy hy hy
 wlw tạ̉ny̱ .. hạystjyb</lyrics>
<author>mnạl smyr, mnạl smyr</author>
